How to use 
 In order to ensure optimal results while using your FOREO LUNA™ 3 Men Deep Facial Cleansing Tool for Skin & Beard, follow these steps:

Dampen your beard or stubble and apply a quality cleanser. Then, dampen your FOREO LUNA™ 3 Men;
Press the button in order to activate cleansing mode;
Cleanse your beard and skin using the device in circular motions;
Turn the device off by pressing and then holding the button for 3 seconds;
Rinse the device, then pat your face and beard dry.

Notes
FOREO LUNA™ devices are compatible with most facial cleansers. However, they should not be used with clay-based, silicone-based, or grainy cleansers, as they may damage the silicone touchpoints.

How to use 
 In order to ensure optimal results while using your FOREO LUNA™ 3 Cleansing & Firming Massage Device for Combination Skin, follow these steps:

Connect your LUNA™ 3 to the FOREO app via Bluetooth. You will need to do this before using your LUNA™ 3 for the first time;
Dampen your face and apply your favorite cleanser to your LUNA™ 3. Then, hit the start button twice;
Use the LUNA™ 3 to massage your face in circular motions, until the built-in timer shuts off;
Rinse your LUNA™ 3 and pat your face dry. Finally, continue with your skincare routine. If you'd like, you can also proceed by using your LUNA™ 3 as a massager and using one of the massage routines built into the FOREO app.

Notes
The FOREO LUNA™ 3 is available in a range of colors, each for a different skin type.
